metadata.name: Scaping from Reality
metadata.description:
Artist: ADARE 
Location: Skógafoss, Iceland.

Scaping From Reality: As wanderers, we are always aiming to escape from reality by seeing places that look unreal and take our breath away.

This piece kicks off my genesis collection: "WNDRLST”

This collection explore that strong feeling/desire to travel that most of us have as wanderers.

Embarking on a journey with no return all along some of Earth's and humanity's most beautiful creations, aiming to be a guidance for travelers.

WNDRLST ®
